Package: localintel
Type: Package
Title: Local Intelligence - Subnational Data Pipeline for Eurostat NUTS Regions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mohamed", "Htitich", 
                  email = "m.ahtitich@outlook.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A comprehensive pipeline for fetching, processing, and visualizing 
    subnational (NUTS 0/1/2) data from Eurostat. Includes functions for cascading 
    data from higher to lower NUTS levels, computing composite health indicators, 
    and creating publication-ready maps. Designed for health system analysis across 
    European regions including health outcomes, enabling environment metrics, 
    and health perception indicators.
